Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Political prisoners
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b040bt6b
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 23 Jul 1978
Russia points the finger at US 'prisoners of conscience' following Ambassador Young's gaffe. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less